    "Sympo ponum makku":["Sympo venuma laddu ku ipo. Serii va polam.. Sympo apo paatha makku ku bday. Athuku munnadi etho fight sanda potu convince aagipom atha makku bekku la va va story ku ena aachu makku bday va apo madam vanthu surprise pannanume makku ah so madam vanthu neraya plan panranga makku ku vanthu bekku saree kaatanum nu solte iruntha aprm intha bekku avanga frnds pesi elam sympo saree kaatalam nu pesi okk nu madam itha secret ah vechu makku ah convince pannidanum nu one month plan ah potu sollave illaye aprm madam nice ah oru vela pannanga apovum yosichirukanum intha makku ena pannanga theriyuma antha saree colour ah eduthu reels anupuna makku intha saree edpi iruku apdi nu doubt vara kudathu nra maari rendu reel anupi ethu nalla iruku nu ketta aprm paatha intha makku la bekku vanthu maroon + purple colour saree ah anupuna atha wear panna pora sympo ku nu apo therila antha colour ah poi okk tha ana innonu tha samaya irukum nu soltan madam reply laiye therinjuthu apo something wrong nu. Aprm sympo ku munnadi sunday apo pesave illa madam apo etho sanda la naa upset ah iruntha night call panni cousin vanthurka ava kita pesitu irukan veladitu irukanu katha madam ku epdi poi solra paarunga soltu intha poiyayum oruthan nambuna paaru avan tha makku athu naa tha aprm call panni makku makku upset ah irukatha pa bday da nalaiku nu pechu serii nu soltu poitu saptu 12 ku varanga madam thunga poranu soltu vantu bday wish pantu paatha thala vali odine irunthurkan anaiku full ah rest um edukala vera aprm tired aagama thala vali varama ena varum sollu enaku kovam tha varum ana ipo story telling mode kolandhaiku soltu kova padalam aprm next day enthu wish pantu clg la vanta naanu madam ah thedine varan naanu avan chudi thana podra so chudi oru colour sonna antha lavendar atha poduvanu sonna atha potu varuva nu thedinu irukan inga paatha girls block la ore crowd sound serii casual ah paatha yaaro saree kaatinu irukanga en laddu maari irunthcha thirumbi paatha en laddee tha paathathum enaku ore kushi epoda meet pannuvom nu irunthchu aprm hall la poitu vanthale viduvana naanu ore kushi la potu kilitu choci la kuduthu mehendi kai la vechathula paathutu apo tha ava lipstick pote paathan kettane nyabagam iruka aprm konjo neram kaatha pesitu photo edutha madam dull ah irukanga yen na sapdala mrng aprm kovam vanchu kova padatha solli convince pantu anupi vita ena lab veraikum vantu aprm eveng aachu balloon kettala enkita naa poi pudingi ava kita kuduthan pona sympo apo ketta en kita apo thara mudila blue colour venum nu intha time kothuoda pudinginu vantane happy ya madam? Aprm corridor la nintu iruntha ivanga la photo eduthunu irunthanga kaval ku nintu iruntha aprm paath thurathula balloon vechutu laddu vara itha pichu kudu makku nu aprm venam soltan elarum vai vechu fill panrupanga nu aprm va photo edukalam nu kuptu photo eduuthu kilitu thirumba nalla pudichu aprm corridor la nadanthu ponom aprm poitu apdiyae ava keela poita naa sem hall ku poitan. Okk va sympo poningala"],
